ments and in sedimentary rocks throughout earth's history. {\textcopyright} 2004 Elsevier Ltd.},
author = {J{\o}rgensen, Bo Barker and B{\"{o}}ttcher, Michael E. and L{\"{u}}schen, Holger and Neretin, Lev N. and Volkov, Igor I.},
