ay for subsequent evolution and diversification of animals. Our study highlights the significance of an integrated approach that combines petrography, mineralogy, and texture-specific micro-drilling geochemistry in chemostratigraphic studies.},
author = {Cui, Huan and Kaufman, Alan J. and Xiao, Shuhai and Zhou, Chuanming and Liu, Xiao Ming},
doi = {10.1016/j.chemgeo.2016.12.010},
file = {:home/nicola/.local/share/data/Mendeley Ltd./Mendeley Desktop/Downloaded/Cui et al. - 2017 - Was the Ediacaran Shuram Excursion a globally synchronized early diagenetic event Insights from methane-derived auth.pdf:pdf},
