e recovery of the biota therefore took a relatively long time. The environmental events at the Permian-Triassic boundary might not be significantly different from those at other Phanerozoic transitions, but they consisted of a series of events that occurred at intervals during the transitional period. ?? 2006 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.},
